<HEADLINE> Amtrak Critic Resigns From Council  </HEADLINE>
By LAURENCE ARNOLD
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON (AP) -- A leading critic of Amtrak resigned Monday
from a panel that oversees the national railway, accusing Amtrak
officials of stonewalling requests for information on its financial
